fields.name: the Conservation Rooflight CR01-3
fields.description: Suitable for pitched roofs* between 17½ and 65 degrees, the Conservation Rooflight is the original low profile skylight, combining the highest modern performance standards with an authentic traditional appearance – external frame colour is Black RAL9005 – internal lining colour is white.
